project_descr: This project aims to enable Montenegro to prepare, produce and disseminate its Third National Communication to the Conference of the Parties of the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change according to Decision 17/CP8 and other guidance provided.

outputs.output_descr: Enable Montenegro to prepare, produce and disseminate its Third National Communication to the Conference of the Parties of the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change according to Decision 17/CP8 and other guidance provided.
